      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a strategy for a new high-end boutique watch line—we're looking at a really premium, $50k+ price point. Can you help me build out a detailed 'ideal customer' persona for this? Like, what do they look like, what's their lifestyle, their career, etc.?",
